         <abstract>
            <p>The Chicago Board Options Exchange currently lists call options for 57 stock issues and the American Stock Exchange call options for 20. The PBW and Pacific Coast Exchanges plan to begin trading in options later this year. To assist portfolio managers in the analysis of what is for them a new investment vehicle, the authors review the historical risk-return experience in options and outline some of the more common uses.</p>
          </abstract>
